'''歐歌鶇'''（[[學名|學名]]：''{{lang|la|Turdus philomelos}}''）是一種分佈在[[歐亞大陸|歐亞大陸]]的[[鶇屬|鶇屬]][[鳥類|鳥類]]，上身呈褪色，下身呈奶白色或淺黃色，有黑色斑點。牠們歌聲獨特，常見於詩歌。

歐歌鶇在[[森林|森林]]、[[花園|花園]]和[[公園|公園]][[繁殖|繁殖]]。牠們會在樹上以泥築巢，每次會生4-5顆蛋。牠們是[[雜食性|雜食性]]的，懂得利用石頭作為[[鐵砧|鐵砧]]攻擊[[蝸牛|蝸牛]]。牠們就像其他[[雀形目|雀形目]]般受體內、外的[[寄生蟲|寄生蟲]]侵襲，且易被[[貓|貓]]和[[猛禽|猛禽]]捕食。

有一部份的歐歌鶇是[[候鳥|候鳥]]，會飛到[[南歐|南歐]]、[[北非|北非]]及[[中東|中東]]過冬。牠們也有被引進到[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]及[[澳洲|澳洲]]。牠們雖然並非[[瀕危|瀕危]]，但在[[歐洲|歐洲]]部份地區的數量大幅減少，可能是與種植業的改變有關。

== 科學分類 ==
=== 命名 ===
歐歌鶇見於[[德國|德國]][[鳥類學|鳥類學家]]Christian Ludwig Brehm1831年的記載，其原[[學名|學名]]一直沿用至今。<ref name= Brehm >{{de icon}}{{cite book en|last=Brehm|first =Christian|title=Handbuch der Naturgeschichte aller Vogel Deutschlands|year=1831|page=382}}</ref>[[種小名|種小名]]是以[[希臘神話|希臘神話]]中的公主[[菲洛墨拉|菲洛墨拉]]來命名，菲洛墨拉的[[舌頭|舌頭]]被割下但卻變成了一隻會唱歌的鳥。<ref name = BTO>{{cite web|title=Song Thrush ''Turdus philomelos'' [CL Brehm, 1831]|work=BTO Birdfacts|url=http://blx1.bto.org/birdfacts/results/bob12000.htm|publisher=British Trust for Ornithology|accessdate=2008-01-25|archive-date=2013-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130401181237/http://blx1.bto.org/birdfacts/results/bob12000.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 分類 ===
[[分子|分子]]研究顯示歐歌鶇是[[槲鶇|槲鶇]]及[[寶興歌鶇|寶興歌鶇]]的近親。這三種是[[鶇屬|鶇屬]]早期的分支，分支出來的時間比牠們多樣化及擴散全球還要早，故與[[烏鶇|烏鶇]]較為疏遠。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=Voelker G, Rohwer S, Bowie RCK, Outlaw DC|year=2007|title=Molecular systematics of a speciose, cosmopolitan songbird genus: Defining the limits of, and relationships among, the ''Turdus'' thrushes|journal=Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution|volume=42|pages=422–34|doi=10.1016/j.ympev.2006.07.016|pmid=16971142|issue=2}}</ref>

[[File:Turdus_philomelos0.jpg|thumb]]的''T. p. clarkei''。]]
歐歌鶇其下有三個[[亞種|亞種]]：
* 指名亞種（''T. p. philomelos''）：佔了大部份的分佈地；
* ''T. p. hebridensis''：由[[英國|英國]][[鳥類學|鳥類學家]]William Eagle Clarke於1913年描述。牠們是一種[[留鳥|留鳥]]，分佈在[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]的[[埃利安錫爾|埃利安錫爾]]及[[斯凱島|斯凱島]]。牠們的顏色最為深色，背部呈深褐色，臀部灰色，上身淡淺黃色，兩側呈灰色。<ref name=Clement/>
* ''T. p. clarkei''：是由[[德國|德國]][[動物學|動物學家]]Ernst Hartert於1909年描述。牠們分佈在[[英國|英國]]及[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]，並在[[法國|法國]]、[[比利時|比利時]]及[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]，有可能也在更東的地區。牠們上身呈褐色，色澤較暖，臀部呈[[橄欖|橄欖]]色，下身呈黃色。牠們是部份[[候鳥|候鳥]]，一些會到法國南部及[[伊比利半島|伊比利半島]]過冬。牠們可以與在[[中歐|中歐]]的指名亞種及在[[內赫布里底群島|內赫布里底群島]]的''T. p. hebridensis''[[混種|混種]]。<ref name= Clement>{{cite book en|title=Thrushes (Helm Identification Guides)|last=Clement|first=Peter|coauthors=Hathway, Ren;  Wilczur, Jan|publisher=Christopher Helm Publishers Ltd|year=2000|pages=392–5|id=ISBN 0-7136-3940-7}}</ref>

另一個[[亞種|亞種]]，如[[西伯利亞|西伯利亞]]的''T. p. nataliae''並未廣泛獲得接受。<ref name=Clement/>

== 特徵 ==
[[File:Song_Thrush_(Turdus_philomelos)_singing_in_tree.jpg|left]]
歐歌鶇長20-23.5厘米及重50-107克。兩性相似，背部呈褐色，下身呈奶白色或淺黃色，有黑色的斑點。翼底及喙呈黃色，腳是粉紅色的。牠們上身的顏色由[[瑞典|瑞典]]至[[西伯利亞|西伯利亞]]逐漸變冷色系。雛鳥像成鳥，但背上及翼底有淺黃色或橙色的斑紋。<ref name=Clement/>

最像歐歌鶇的[[物種|物種]]是[[白眉歌鶇|白眉歌鶇]]，但牠們的眉是白色，兩側紅色。[[槲鶇|槲鶇]]較大，尾巴呈白色；[[寶興歌鶇|寶興歌鶇]]雖然[[羽毛|羽毛]]相似，但面上有黑色斑紋，而且分佈地也不重疊。<ref name=Clement/>

{{listen|filename=Turdus philomelos 816.ogg|title=歐歌鶇叫聲|description=}}
歐歌鶇的叫聲短而尖銳，遷徙時會發出薄而高音的叫聲。警報聲會隨著危險而變得短及刺耳。雄鳥在樹上、天台或其他高位的叫聲是清晰的歌聲。在[[埃利安錫爾|埃利安錫爾]]的群落一般會在2月至6月間發出這種叫聲，而其他[[亞種|亞種]]則要到11月至7月才發出這種叫聲。<ref name=Clement/>牠們是叫聲最大的[[鳥類|鳥類]]之一。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=Brackenbury, J. H.|year=1979|title=Power capabilities of the avian sound-producing system|journal=J. Exp. Biology|volume=78|pages=163–6|url=http://jeb.biologists.org/cgi/reprint/78/1/163.pdf|format=PDF|access-date=2010-07-02|archive-date=2008-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081010143657/http://jeb.biologists.org/cgi/reprint/78/1/163.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

雄鳥的歌聲可以多達100種劇目<ref>{{cite journal en|title=Relations between Song Repertoire Size and the Volume of Brain Nuclei Related to Song: Comparative Evolutionary Analyses amongst Oscine Birds.|first=Timothy J.|last=Devoogd|coauthors=John R. Krebs, Susan D. Healy, Andy Purvis|journal=Proceedings: Biological Sciences|volume=254|year=1993|pages=75–82|doi=10.1098/rspb.1993.0129|issue=1340}}</ref>，大部份都是由父母處及鄰近的[[鳥類|鳥類]]抄來。模仿聲包括人造的[[電話|電話]]聲<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Slater|first=Peter J. B.|year=1983|title=The Buzby phenomenon: Thrushes and telephones|journal=Animal Behavior|volume=31|pages=308–309|doi=10.1016/S0003-3472(83)80204-8}}</ref>，牠們也會重覆飼養鳥類的叫聲，如[[白臉樹鴨|白臉樹鴨]]。<ref name=Clement/>

== 分佈及棲息地 ==
[[File:Song_Thrush-Mindaugas_Urbonas-2c.jpg|thumb]]的指名亞種。]]
歐歌鶇在大部份[[歐洲|歐洲]]地區（但不包括大部份[[伊比利半島|伊比利半島]]、[[義大利|義大利]]低地或[[希臘|希臘]]南部）、經[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]及[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]至[[貝加爾湖|貝加爾湖]][[繁殖|繁殖]]。牠們在[[挪威|挪威]]分佈至[[北緯|北緯]]75°，但在[[西伯利亞|西伯利亞]]卻只達北緯60°。從[[斯堪地那維亞|斯堪地那維亞]]、[[東歐|東歐]]及俄羅斯而來的歐歌鶇會到[[地中海|地中海]]、[[北非|北非]]及[[中東|中東]]過冬，但在西部的只有一些會離開自己的地方。<ref name=Clement/>

指名亞種於1860年及1880年由馴化協會引入到[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]及[[澳洲|澳洲]]。<ref name=ENZ>{{cite web|title='BIRDS', from ''An Encyclopaedia of New Zealand'', edited by A. H. McLintock, originally published in 1966|work=Te Ara - The Encyclopedia of New Zealand, updated 18-Sep-2007|url=http://www.TeAra.govt.nz/1966/B/Birds/en|publisher=Ministry for Culture and Heritage / Te Manatū Taonga|accessdate=2008-03-13|archive-date=2008-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080907230418/http://www.teara.govt.nz/1966/B/Birds/en|dead-url=no}}</ref>歐歌鶇在新西蘭快速適應及擴展至周邊的[[島嶼|島嶼]]，如[[克馬德克群島|克馬德克群島]]、[[查塔姆群島|查塔姆群島]]及[[奧克蘭群島|奧克蘭群島]]。<ref name=NZ>{{cite book en|last=Heather, B.|coauthors=Robertson, H.|title=The Field Guide to the Birds of New Zealand|year=1996|publisher=Viking|location=Auckland|id=ISBN 0-670-89370-6|pages=384–5}}</ref>不過牠們在澳洲只限於在[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]附近的地方。<ref name=Oz>{{cite web|title=Song thrush (''Turdus philomelos'')|work=Birds|url=http://www.agric.wa.gov.au/content/pw/vp/bird/songthrush.htm|publisher=Department of Agriculture, Western Australia|accessdate=2008-01-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071208062121/http://www.agric.wa.gov.au/content/PW/VP/BIRD/songthrush.htm|archivedate=2007-12-08}}</ref>歐歌鶇在新西蘭掠食[[無脊椎動物|無脊椎動物]]造成一定影響<ref name=snail>{{cite web |title=The State of Our Invertebrate Animals |work=State of New Zealand's Environment 1997, Chapter 9 |url=http://www.mfe.govt.nz/publications/ser/ser1997/html/chapter9.7.2.html |publisher=Ministry for the Environment, New Zealand |accessdate=2008-03-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080617225326/http://www.mfe.govt.nz/publications/ser/ser1997/html/chapter9.7.2.html |archivedate=2008-06-17 }}</ref>，而牠們也對果園造成商業損失。<ref name=DAFWA>{{cite web|title=Song thrush (''Turdus philomelos'')|url=http://www.agric.wa.gov.au/content/PW/VP/BIRD/songthrush.htm|publisher=Department of Agriculture and Food Western Australia|accessdate=2008-03-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071208062121/http://www.agric.wa.gov.au/content/PW/VP/BIRD/songthrush.htm|archivedate=2007-12-08}}</ref>歐歌鶇在新西蘭作為[[入侵物種|入侵物種]]，故沒有法律保障。<ref name=MENZ>{{cite web|title=The State of Our Indigenous Birds |work=The State of Our Biodiversity - The State of New Zealand’s Environment |url=http://www.mfe.govt.nz/publications/ser/ser1997/chap9-2-2.pdf |format=PDF |publisher=Ministry for the Environment, New Zealand |accessdate=2008-03-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150124211015/http://mfe.govt.nz/publications/ser/ser1997/chap9-2-2.pdf |archivedate=2015-01-24 }}</ref>

歐歌鶇一般棲息在有草叢及鄰近開放地方的[[森林|森林]]，而在[[西歐|西歐]]則也會棲息在[[花園|花園]]及[[公園|公園]]。牠們可以在[[林木線|林木線]][[繁殖|繁殖]]，在[[瑞士|瑞士]]就可達2200米。''T. p. hebridensis''會在較為開放的郊野繁殖，包括荒原；而在東部的指名亞種則只限於茂密的[[針葉林|針葉林]]內繁殖。<ref name=Clement/>[[英國|英國]]一項研究發現歐歌鶇的分佈地只有3.5%是農地，而花園則佔了71.5%。餘下的則是林地。<ref name=Mason>{{cite journal en|last=Mason|first=Christopher F.|year=1998|title=Habitats of the Song Thrush ''Turdus philomelos'' in a largely arable landscape|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-zoology_1998-01_244/page/89|journal=Journal of Zoology|volume=244|pages=89–93|doi=10.1111/j.1469-7998.1998.tb00010.x}}</ref>牠們過冬的地方與繁殖地相近，但不會在高原及其他開放的地方。<ref name=BWP/>不過''T. p. hebridensis''會經常走到海岸過冬。<ref name=Clement/>

== 行為 ==
[[File:Song_Thrush_cracking_a_snail_shell.ogv|thumb]]殼的歐歌鶇。]]
歐歌鶇並不經常聚居，有時在[[冬天|冬天]]或環境適合覓食時才會走在一起，也有可能與[[烏鶇|烏鶇]]、[[田鶇|田鶇]]或[[白眉歌鶇|白眉歌鶇]]一起生活。<ref name=Clement/>牠們傾向回到同一過冬的地區。<ref name=BWP/>

歐歌鶇是[[一夫一妻制|一夫一妻制]]的。在會遷徙的地區，雄鳥回到[[繁殖|繁殖]]地後會重新設立地盤及開始唱歌；而在其他地區，雄鳥會全年留在自己的地盤，間中唱歌，但雌鳥可能會自行設立過冬的地點，直至於初春時配對在一起。<ref name=BWP/>

在遷徙時，歐歌鶇主要在夜間展開旅程，並採取直接及強烈的飛行行動。牠們會以鬆散的小群橫渡[[海洋|海洋]]，並經常互相呼叫保持聯繫。<ref name=Clement/>在較北部的歐歌鶇會於4月至8月進行遷徙，而大部份的因路程較短，則會在9月至12月中旬才南下。惡劣的[[氣候|氣候]]可以使牠們遷徙得更遠。回程的時間各有不同，如在[[地中海|地中海]]的是約在2月中旬，而[[瑞典|瑞典]]北部及[[西伯利亞|西伯利亞]]中部的則會在5月。<ref name=Clement/>在[[格陵蘭|格陵蘭]]、多個[[大西洋|大西洋]][[島嶼|島嶼]]及[[西非|西非]]曾發現一些離群的份子。<ref name=Clement/>

=== 繁殖及生存 ===
[[File:Turdus_philomelos_-Apenheul_Primate_Park,_Netherlands_-eggs-8.jpg|upright]]。]]
雌性歐歌鶇會在灌木、樹或蔓上築巢，''T. p. hebridensis''則會在地上築巢。牠們會以泥及乾草築巢。雌鳥每次會生4-5顆蛋，鳥蛋呈鮮藍色，有些少黑色或紫色的斑點<ref name=Clement/>，蛋約有2.7 x 2.0厘米大小及重6克，當中6%為蛋殼。<ref name=BTO/>雌鳥會獨自孵蛋10-17日；孵化後10-17日雛鳥就會換羽。牠們每年一般生2-3次蛋，但在北部地區的可能只有一隻雛鳥能仍長。<ref name=Clement/>平均而言，54.6%的[[英國|英國]]雛鳥於首年仍然生存，成年的每年生存率為62.2%。牠們的壽命為3年，但最老的可以老達10歲8個月。<ref name=BTO/>

[[File:Song_Thrush_(Turdus_philomelos)_with_chicks_in_nest.jpg|right]]
歐歌鶇有時會成為[[大杜鵑|大杜鵑]]等的[[寄主|寄主]]，但此情況很罕有，因牠們能夠發現杜鵑鳥蛋的不同。<ref name=BB95>{{cite journal en|last=Davies|first=N. B.|title=Cuckoo tricks with eggs and chicks|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_british-birds_2002-03_95_3/page/101|journal=British Birds|volume=95|issue=3|pages=101–15|date=March 2002}}</ref>不過，牠們不會帶有與[[烏鶇|烏鶇]]相同的攻擊性對付成年杜鵑。<ref name=Grim>{{cite journal en|last=Grim|first=Tomáŝ|coauthors=Honza, Marcel|year=2001|url=http://www.zoologie.upol.cz/osoby/Grim/Grim_&_Honza_Biologia_2001.pdf|title=Differences in behaviour of closely related thrushes (''Turdus philomelos'' and ''T. merula'') to experimental parasitism by the common cuckoo ''Cuculus canorus''|format=PDF|journal=Biologia, Bratislava|volume=56|issue=5|pages=549–56|author=|access-date=2018-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809020603/http://www.zoologie.upol.cz/osoby/Grim/Grim_%26_Honza_Biologia_2001.pdf|archive-date=2017-08-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]入侵的歐歌鶇在以往超過130年間都能分辨非偽裝的鳥蛋。<ref name=JAB>{{cite journal en|last=Hale|first=Katrina|coauthors=Briskie, James V.|url=http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.0908-8857.2007.03734.x|title=Response of introduced European birds in New Zealand to experimental brood parasitism|journal=Journal of Avian Biology|volume=38|issue=2|pages=198–204|doi=10.1111/j.0908-8857.2007.03734.x|date=March 2007|author=|access-date=2010-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215174815/http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.0908-8857.2007.03734.x|archive-date=2018-12-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

[[貓|貓]]、[[縱紋腹小鴞|縱紋腹小鴞]]及[[雀鷹|雀鷹]]等會掠食成年歐歌鶇；[[喜鵲|喜鵲]]、[[松鴉|松鴉]]及[[灰松鼠|灰松鼠]]也會掠食鳥蛋及雛鳥。<ref name=Brown>{{cite web|last=Brown |first=Roy |title=A Review of the impact of Mammalian Predators on Farm Songbird Population Dynamics |url=http://www.songbird-survival.org.uk/media/songbird-review-7-06.pdf |publisher=Songbird Survival |format=PDF |accessdate=2008-01-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070702155628/http://www.songbird-survival.org.uk/media/songbird-review-7-06.pdf |archivedate=2007-07-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=RSPB>{{cite web|title=Song thrush|work=Birds and wildlife|url=http://www.rspb.org.uk/wildlife/birdguide/name/s/songthrush/threats.asp|publisher=RSPB|accessdate=2008-01-27|archive-date=2009-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090426062631/http://rspb.org.uk/wildlife/birdguide/name/s/songthrush/threats.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=NatEng/>就像其他的[[雀形目|雀形目]]，歐歌鶇也有[[寄生蟲|寄生蟲]]，如[[線蟲動物門|線蟲動物門]]的''Splendidofilaria (Avifilaria) mavis''。<ref name=nematode>{{es icon}}{{cite journal en|last=Martil|first=S. Cano|coauthors=Caballero, E.J. López; del Valle Portilla, María T|month=|year=2000|url=http://revistas.mes.edu.cu:9900/eduniv/03-Revistas-Cientificas/Biologia/2000/1/11000101.pdf|title=Estudio con microscopia electrónica de barrido de adultos de ''Splendidofilaria (Avifilaria) Mavis'' (Leiper, 1909) Anderson, 1961.|format=PDF|journal=Revista biologia|volume=14|issue=1|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318113846/http://revistas.mes.edu.cu:9900/eduniv/03-Revistas-Cientificas/Biologia/2000/1/11000101.pdf|archivedate=2009-03-18}}</ref>一項[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]有關[[血液|血液]]寄生蟲的研究顯示所有[[田鶇|田鶇]]、[[白眉歌鶇|白眉歌鶇]]及歐歌鶇含有[[變形血原蟲屬|變形血原蟲屬]]及[[錐蟲屬|錐蟲屬]]。<ref name=Markovets>{{cite journal en|url=http://images.katalogas.lt/maleidykla/Eko54/Eko_008_012N.pdf |format=PDF |last=Palinauskas |first=Vaidas |coauthors=Markovets, Mikhail Yu; Kosarev, Vladislav V; Efremov, Vladislav D; Sokolov Leonid V; Valkiûnas, Gediminas |year=2005 |title=Occurrence of avian haematozoa in Ekaterinburg and Irkutsk districts of Russia |journal=Ekologija |volume=4 |pages=8–12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090326090558/http://images.katalogas.lt/maleidykla/Eko54/Eko_008_012N.pdf |archivedate=2009-03-26 }}</ref>[[硬蜱屬|硬蜱屬]]也很普遍，牠們也會帶有[[病原體|病原體]]，包括在俄羅斯、[[東歐|東歐]]及[[中歐|中歐]][[森林|森林]]地區的[[腦炎|腦炎]]<ref name=Pentagon>Fedorov, Yu. V. (1968) [http://stinet.dtic.mil/cgi-bin/GetTRDoc?AD=AD672664&Location=U2&doc=GetTRDoc.pdf "Further observations on the significance of wild birds as hosts of ''Ixodes'' ticks in the Tomsk focus of tick-borne encephalitis"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225124752/http://stinet.dtic.mil/cgi-bin/GetTRDoc?AD=AD672664&Location=U2&doc=GetTRDoc.pdf |date=2009-02-25 }} ''Pentagon Reports'' Number: 0916176 (PDF)</ref>，與及較為普遍的[[疏螺旋體屬|疏螺旋體屬]]。<ref name=Kipp>{{cite journal en|last=Kipp|first=Susanne|coauthors=Goedecke,  Andreas; Dorn, Wolfram; Wilske, Bettina; VolkeFingerle|title=Role of birds in Thuringia, Germany, in the natural cycle of ''Borrelia burgdorferi'' sensu lato, the Lyme disease spirochaete|journal=International Journal of Medical Microbiology|volume=296|pages=125–8|doi=10.1016/j.ijmm.2006.01.001|pmid=16530003|date=May 2006}}</ref>一些疏螺旋體屬的[[物種|物種]]會引起[[萊姆病|萊姆病]]，而歐歌鶇等在地上覓食的雀鳥則是此病的溫床。<ref name=EID>{{cite journal en|last=Comstedt|first=Pär|coauthors=Bergström, Sven: Olsen, Björn; Garpmo, Ulf; Marjavaara, Lisette; Mejlon, Hans; Barbour, Alan G. and Bunikis, Jonas|title=Migratory Passerine Birds as Reservoirs of Lyme Borreliosis in Europe|url=http://www.cdc.gov/ncidod/EID/vol12no07/pdfs/vol12no07.pdf|journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases|format=PDF|volume=12|issue=7|pages=1087–94|date=July 2006|author=|access-date=2010-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101011081438/http://www.cdc.gov/ncidod/eid/vol12no07/pdfs/vol12no07.pdf|archive-date=2010-10-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 覓食 ===
[[File:Song_Thrush_(Turdus_philomelos)_with_worms_in_beak_on_grass.jpg|left]]的歐歌鶇。]]
歐歌鶇是[[雜食性|雜食性]]的，吃多種[[無脊椎動物|無脊椎動物]]，尤其是[[蚯蚓|蚯蚓]]及[[蝸牛|蝸牛]]，也會吃軟[[果實|果實]]及[[草莓|草莓]]。牠們會以[[視覺|視覺]]來尋找獵物，或會在葉堆中尋找潛在食物。<ref name=Clement/>

當在乾旱或惡劣的環境下，蝸牛是歐歌鶇重要的食物。牠們會用石頭來敲碎蝸牛的殼，抽出軟體部份，並將之放在地上擦。<ref name=BWP/>幼鳥最初會學習拋物件，直至懂得使用工具來敲碎蝸牛殼。<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Henty|first=C. J.|year=1986|title=Development of snail-smashing by song thrushes|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_british-birds_1986-06_79_6/page/277|journal=British Birds|volume=79|pages=277–81}}</ref>雛鳥主要吃[[動物|動物]]食物，如[[蠕蟲|蠕蟲]]、[[蛞蝓|蛞蝓]]、蝸牛及[[昆蟲|昆蟲]][[幼蟲|幼蟲]]。<ref name=Clement/>

[[二樹叢蝸牛|二樹叢蝸牛]]經常被歐歌鶇所掠食，它們多態的殼被認為是為了減低掠食而進化的。<ref name=Goodhart>{{cite journal en|last=Goodhart|first= C. B.|title=Thrush Predation on the Snail Cepaea hortensis |journal= The Journal of Animal Ecology|volume=27|issue=1|pages=47–57|doi=10.2307/2173|date=May 1958}}</ref>不過，歐歌鶇並非唯一的[[掠食者|掠食者]]。<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Owen|first=Denis F.|coauthors=Sven-Axel Bengtson|year=1972|title=Polymorphism in the Land Snail ''Cepaea Hortensis'' in Iceland.|journal=Oikos|volume=23|issue=2|pages=218–25|doi=10.2307/3543409}}</ref>

== 保育狀況 ==
歐歌鶇的分佈地很廣，估計達1000萬平方公里，單在[[歐洲|歐洲]]的數量就估計有4000-7100萬隻。<ref name="iucn"/>

在[[古北界|古北界]]西部，有證據顯示數量下降，但並未達至保育的水平，故[[世界自然保護聯盟|世界自然保護聯盟]]將之列為[[無危|無危]]。<ref name="iucn"/>在[[英國|英國]]及[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]，牠們的數量就下降了50%。<ref name=BWP>{{cite book en|last=Snow|first=David|coauthors=Perrins, Christopher M  (editors)|title=The Birds of the Western Palearctic concise edition (2 volumes)|publisher=Oxford University Press|year=1998|location=Oxford|id=ISBN 0-19-854099-X|pages=1225–8}}</ref><ref name=BTO2>{{cite web|title=Song Thrush ''Turdus philomelos'' |work=Breeding Birds in the Wider Countryside |url=http://www.bto.org/birdtrends2007/wcrsonth.htm |publisher=British Trust for Ornithology/Joint Nature Conservation Committee |accessdate=2008-01-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080617092859/http://www.bto.org/birdtrends2007/wcrsonth.htm |archivedate=2008-06-17|deadurl=yes }}</ref>在農地上的數量下降得最厲害，相信是與種植業的改變有關。<ref name=Cocker>{{cite book en|last=Cocker|first=Mark|coauthors=Mabey, Richard|title=Birds Britannica|year=2005|location=London|publisher=Chatto & Windus|id=ISBN 0-7011-6907-9|pages=355–9}}</ref>真實原因但卻不明，也有可能與樹籬的消失或加劇使用[[殺蟲劑|殺蟲劑]]有關。這種改變令食物的供應減少。<ref name=ukbap>{{cite web|title=Song Thrush (''Turdus philomelos'') |work=Species Action Plan |url=http://www.ukbap.org.uk/UKPlans.aspx?ID=621#2 |publisher=UK Biodiversity Action Plan |accessdate=2008-03-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080415111704/http://www.ukbap.org.uk/UKPlans.aspx?ID=621 |archivedate=2008-04-15 }}</ref>在[[花園|花園]]，使用毒餌來控制[[蛞蝓|蛞蝓]]及[[蝸牛|蝸牛]]也對歐歌鶇造成危害。<ref name=NatEng>{{cite web|title=Song thrush - ''Turdus philomelos''|work=Gardening with Wildlife in Mind|url=http://www.plantpress.com/wildlife/o31-songthrush.php|publisher=Natural England|accessdate=2008-01-28|archive-date=2009-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090815015839/http://www.plantpress.com/wildlife/o31-songthrush.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[城市|城市]]，牠們也成為了[[路殺|路殺]]。<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Erritzoe|first=J.|coauthors=Mazgajski T. D., Rejt L.|year=2003|title=Bird casualties on European roads — a review.|journal=Acta Ornithol.|volume=38|pages=77–93|url=http://www.birdresearch.dk/unilang/articles/traffic.pdf|format=PDF|access-date=2010-07-02|archive-date=2017-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809030952/http://www.birdresearch.dk/unilang/articles/traffic.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 文化 ==
[[托馬斯·哈代|托馬斯·哈代]]<ref name=stallings>{{cite web|author=Stallings, A. E. |title=The Darkling Thrush: A Centennial Appreciation |url=http://www.alsopreview.com/aside/aethrush.html |accessdate=2008-03-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080519095858/http://www.alsopreview.com/aside/aethrush.html |archivedate=2008-05-19|deadurl=yes }}</ref>、[[泰德·休斯|泰德·休斯]]<ref name=thrushes>{{cite web|title=Thrushes|work=Poems by Ted Hughes|url=http://www.poemhunter.com/poem/thrushes/|publisher=Poemhunter|accessdate=2008-03-11|archive-date=2019-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190522125409/https://www.poemhunter.com/poem/thrushes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>及[[威廉·華茲華斯|威廉·華茲華斯]]<ref name=Wordsworth>{{cite web|title=The Tables Turned|work=William Wordsworth: Complete Poetical Works|url=http://www.bartleby.com/145/ww134.html|publisher=bartleby.com|accessdate=2008-01-29|archive-date=2008-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080203101613/http://www.bartleby.com/145/ww134.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>也在其詩中描述了歐歌鶇。

=== 食物 ===
歐歌鶇最早於12000年前被捕獵作為食物<ref>{{cite journal en|last=Bocheñski|first=Z.|coauthors=Tomek T.|year=2004|title=Bird remains from a rock-shelter in Krucza Skala (Central Poland)|journal=Acta zooologica cracoviensia|volume=47|issue=1-2|pages=27–47|url=http://www.isez.pan.krakow.pl/journals/azc_v/pdf/47(1-2)/04.pdf|format=PDF|access-date=2010-07-02|archive-date=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727201441/http://www.isez.pan.krakow.pl/journals/azc_v/pdf/47(1-2)/04.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，在《[[奧德賽|奧德賽]]》也有記載。<ref name=Homer>{{cite book en|last=Homer|coauthors=Fagles, Robert (translator)|title=The Odyssey|year=1997|publisher=Penguin Books|location=New York|id=ISBN 0-14-026886-3|pages=453}}</ref>在[[地中海|地中海]]一直至今也有捕獵牠們，但並非牠們在某些地區真正減少的原因。<ref name=Cocker/>

在[[西班牙|西班牙]]仍然有用粘鳥膠來捕捉歐歌鶇。<ref name="case c79">{{cite web|url=http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=CELEX:62003J0079:EN:HTML|title=Failure of a Member State to fulfil obligations – Directive 79/409/EEC – Conservation of wild birds – Hunting using limed twigs - Summary of the Judgment|author=Commission of the European Communities|date=9 December 2004|access-date=2010-07-02|archive-date=2019-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190526140610/https://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=CELEX%3A62003J0079%3AEN%3AHTML|dead-url=no}}</ref>於2003年及2004年，[[歐盟|歐盟]]嘗試禁止這種捕獵方法，但不成功。<ref name="parany1">{{es icon}}{{cite web|url=http://www.lasprovincias.es/valencia/prensa/20061214/cvalenciana/entramado-para-cazar-tordos_20061214.html|title=Un entramado para cazar tordos|author=Las Provincias|date=14 December 2006|accessdate=2010-07-02|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212615/http://www.lasprovincias.es/valencia/prensa/20061214/cvalenciana/entramado-para-cazar-tordos_20061214.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="parany2">{{es icon}}{{cite web|url=http://www.lukor.com/not-neg/sectores/0412/09121501.htm |title=El Tribunal de la UE condena a España por permitir la caza con 'parany' en la Comunidad Valenciana |author=Europa Press |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080614164958/http://www.lukor.com/not-neg/sectores/0412/09121501.htm |archivedate=2008-06-14 }}</ref>

=== 寵物 ===
歐歌鶇最少於19世紀就已經被捕捉作為寵物。<ref name=Dyson>{{cite book en|last=Dyson|first=C. E.|title=Bird-Keeping - A Practical Guide for the Management of Singing and Cage Birds|url=https://archive.org/details/birdkeepingpract00dysorich|year=1889|publisher=Frederick Warne and co|pages=[https://archive.org/details/birdkeepingpract00dysorich/page/51 51]}}</ref>同樣地也沒有證據顯示捕捉牠們作為寵物令其數量下降。<ref name= Clement/>

